premise_source_doc_sentence: Karlie Elizabeth Kloss  (  born August 3 , 1992  )  is an American fashion model .
She was a Victoria 's Secret Angel from 2011 to 2014 .
The 16th fashion show featured some the new Angels  (  Karlie Kloss being the only newcomer to have three outfits  )  and also the returning Angels .

She appeared in British Elle editorial in August 2008 for the first time , in September 2008 , she appeared in Chinese Vogue editorial , alongside Karlie Kloss and Hanne Gaby Odiele , and walked Victoria 's Secret Fashion Show in November 2012 for the first time .
Karlie Kloss  (  born 1992  )  , American fashion model

The show features some of the world 's leading fashion models , such as current Victoria 's Secret Angels Adriana Lima , Alessandra Ambrosio , Doutzen Kroes , Candice Swanepoel , Lily Aldridge , Lindsay Ellingson , Karlie Kloss , and Behati Prinsloo .
The show was opened by supermodel Karlie Kloss , and celebrities in attendance included Uma Thurman , Christina Ricci , Michelle Dockery , Christina Hendricks , Graydon Carter , and Fran Lebowitz .
